service.name: Newborn Supplement
service.description: Newborn Supplement (NBS) helps families with the additional costs of caring for a newborn or adopted child. It can be paid for a child born, or entrusted to care as part of an adoption process, on or after 1 March 2014. It replaces Baby Bonus (BBY). NBS is an add-on component of a customer's Family Tax Benefit (FTB) Part A entitlement for up to 13 weeks (or 91 days).
